column2: SELECT spec.specobjId, spec.plate, spec.mjd, spec.fiberid, spec.ra, spec.dec, spec.z, spec.zErr, galspec.h_beta_eqw, galspec.h_beta_flux/galspec.oiii_#_flux, spec.class, spec.subclass INTO MYDB.MyTable_SIII_# FROM SpecObjAll as spec JOIN galSpecLine as galspec on galspec.specobjid = spec.specobjid WHERE spec.z < # and galspec.h_beta_eqw < # and galspec.h_beta_eqw/galspec.h_beta_eqw_err < # and galspec.oiii_#_flux/galspec.oiii_#_flux_err > # and spec.class = # ORDER BY spec.plate
